We are pumped to see the Czechs tonight in the World Baseball Classic. My brother @sashadrzak47 is their hitting coach and they are a great underdog story. The qualifier they lost the first game and then won out against teams like Spain and Germany who were loaded full of mlb guys and ended up hitting 11 💣’s and the next best team had 6. They open tonight against China then they play Japan, Australia and Korea. Czechs have one guy who is joining them who played in MLB the rest of the team are all Czech guys who play in the Czech baseball league and have normal jobs too. As long as you don’t finish last you get into the next world baseball classic without having to go through the qualifier. Let’s cheer on @baseballczech and see if they can make a little run in the WBC.  #wbc #worldbaseballclassic #czechbaseball #mlb

Ladies and Gentlemen now batting the Twang Town Tater the Nashville Nuke, Little Big Fly himself Dawson Logan Lee Derhak! Welcome to the tribe son. 
I went to bed at midnight last night/this am and I said is tonight the night Andrea said IDK I’m feeling a little off but maybe just cuz of my Dr apt today. She said try and get some sleep. I said alight just slap me on the back if we gotta roll. 1am she slaps me on the back and says I think it’s happening. Got up grabbed our things heading into the hospital on no sleep for both of us. Absolutely no traffic at that hour which was great. Got to the hospital and every nurse was awesome…they thought the baby was coming fast so they called our Dr in at 3:30am then she started to slow down a little bit so the Dr just went to her office to rest a bit. What a legend for showing up for us when it mattered. After being up in labor all night with our nurse the Doc and her team finished the job at 9:14am. We feel extremely blessed and thankful for our new little dude and the St. Thomas staff here in Nashville. Mom and baby are healthy. It was so great to see Emmy meet him for the first time and whisper to him you’re gonna be my best friend forever. One of the three greatest days of my life! Andrea is a rockstar. She did such a good job on no sleep. Really flexed her superpowers. #newbaby
